OL,4,CMartin's Law launched
OL,6,FA into new legislation for better
OL,7,Fprotection against terror attacks in
OL,8,Fpublic places has been launched.
OL,10,FKnown as '', it is named after Martyn
OL,11,FHett, one of 22 people killed in the
OL,12,F2017 Manchester attack.
OL,14,FThe Home Office said the new laws
OL,15,Fwould require venues to take steps to
OL,16,Fkeep the public safe.
OL,18,FIt said it make sure the public is
OL,19,Fprotected without putting "unnecessary
OL,20,Fburdens on smaller businesses".
