OL,3,CSix-week consultation into anti-terror
OL,4,CMartin's Law launched
OL,6,FUnder the proposed law, premises will
OL,7,Fbe considered 'standard tier' or
OL,8,F'enhanced tier'.
OL,10,FWhat are the tiers?
OL,12,FVenues will need to undertake low-cost
OL,13,Feffective measures such as training,
OL,14,Finformation sharing, and completion of
OL,15,Fa preparedness plan.
OL,17,FVenues will be required to undertake
OL,18,Fan additional risk assessment that
OL,19,Fwill inform the development and
OL,20,Fimplementation of a thorough security
OL,21,Fplan.
