OL,4,CMartin's Law launched
OL,6,FMartyn Hett's mother Figen Murray has .
OL,8,FMs Murray, who was appointed an OBE
OL,9,Ffor her work in counterterrorism said
OL,10,Furged venues and small businesses to
OL,11,Frespond to the consultation.
OL,13,FSecurity Minister Tom Tugendhat said:
OL,15,F"Simple steps save lives. Martyn's Law
OL,16,Fwill help protect the British public
OL,17,Ffrom terrorism, and make sure public
OL,18,Fpremises are better prepared in the
OL,19,Fevent of a terror attack.
