OL,6,F"I want to make sure that our
OL,7,Fproposals are balanced and
OL,8,Fproportionate. That's why our updated
OL,9,Fapproach is easy to implement, and
OL,10,Fbetter tailored to individual
OL,11,Fbusinesses.
OL,13,F"I'd encourage smaller premises to
OL,14,Fshare their feedback on these crucial
OL,15,Fchanges. Your feedback will help
OL,16,Fensure that Martyn's Law stands the
OL,17,Ftest of time."
