OL,6,FThe Home Office said a Martyn's Law
OL,7,Fregulator will be established to
OL,8,Fmonitor compliance and advise premises
OL,9,Fwithin scope of the legislation.
OL,11,FIt said following the conclusion of
OL,12,Fthe consultation process on 18 March,
OL,13,Fthe bill will be introduced as soon as
OL,14,Fparliamentary time allows.
